{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7ca4cec560","title":"告同学书","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"199ca10b88","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"7ca4cec560"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"765ec99bb5","name":"龙英华"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ce7e87f546","type":"title","text":"告同学书","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7ca4cec560"},{"id":"a3ba919b3b","type":"authors","text":"北京大学龙英华","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7ca4cec560"},{"id":"1d340777b7","type":"subtitle","text":"（龙英华：北京大学哲学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7ca4cec560"},{"id":"fd4591da9f","type":"subtitle","text":"新的伊甸——告同学书","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7ca4cec560"},{"id":"bb7ed51534","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林同志对付正直的共产党员的办法有被我国的反社会主义、反民主分子采用的危险。匈牙利的工人阶级的叛徒格罗对付工人阶级的办法也有被我国的反民主分子采用的危险。中国的反民主势力力图把反资产阶级右派的斗争扩大为镇压社会主义民主运动的斗争。社会主义民主运动是中国工人阶级劳动人民劳动知识分子青年学生参加党整风运动基本形式。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7ca4cec560"},{"id":"ec25a57648","type":"paragraph","text":"我也面对着反民主势力的迫害，不能不写——〈告同学书〉，以便在必要的时候获得党中央和同学们的支持。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7ca4cec560"},{"id":"81ce7c334d","type":"paragraph","text":" 龙英华","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7ca4cec560"}],"page":{"id":"ddba7b753a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7ca4cec560","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}